<h1>About Us</h1>

<p>Welcome to our online calculator website.</p>

<p>Our website is designed to provide free, fast, and easy-to-use online calculators for everyone. Currently, we offer a BMI (Body Mass Index) calculator that helps users understand their body weight status based on height and weight.</p>

<p>Our goal is to create simple tools that are accessible on all devices without any registration or cost.</p>

<p>We continuously work to improve our calculators and add more useful tools in the future.</p>

<p>Thank you for visiting our website.</p>

